title: Maharaja
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Salad bar, Take-out, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegedrom changed name to Maharaja in Aug 2015. Indian and Nepali cuisine restaurant offering some vegetarian dishes using seitan (wheat meat), tofu, soy cheese, vegetable stir-fry. Has a self-service salad bar. Large range of curries. Part of the restaurant has traditional seating on pillows around low tables.
